others I will respect their decisions.</p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\">In this world of polarised opinions this is surely the only way to move forward, to give each other respect, to listen<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">¬† </span>and to accept that we may be wrong.</p>\r\n\r\n<blockquote>\r\n<p class=\"p3\"><span class=\"s1\">In every truth the opposite is equally true.¬†</span><span class=\"s2\">That is to say, any truth can only be expressed and put into words when it is one-sided. Everything that can be thought with the mind and said with words is one-sided, it\'s all just the half of it, lacking completeness, roundness, or unity.</span></p>\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<p class=\"p3\"><span class=\"s2\"> Siddhartha by Hermann Hesse</span></p>'),(748,132,'_sub_text','field_57e90fea19072'),(749,131,'hero_image','grains.jpeg'),(750,131,'_hero_image','field_57d2bacfc7bdd'),(751,131,'intro','I have been consuming a vegan diet for the past year. I made the decision for ethical reasons due to my concerns with animal mistreatment and the strain that animal based diets places on the environment.\r\n\r\n'),(752,131,'_intro','field_57ebd1b41c03b'),(753,131,'sub_text','<p class=\"p1\">Rather than being vegan we should be eating¬†consciously.</p>'),(754,131,'_sub_text','field_57e90fea19072'),(756,134,'hero_image','grains.jpeg'),(757,134,'_hero_image','field_57d2bacfc7bdd'),(758,134,'intro','I have been a consuming a vegan diet for the past year. I made the decision for ethical reason due to my concerns with animal mistreatment and the strain that animal based diets places on the environment.\r\n\r\n'),(759,134,'_intro','field_57ebd1b41c03b'),(760,134,'sub_text','<p class=\"p1\">Rather than being vegan we should be eating¬†consciously.</p>'),(761,134,'_sub_text','field_57e90fea19072'),(763,135,'hero_image','grains.jpeg'),(764,135,'_hero_image','field_57d2bacfc7bdd'),(765,135,'intro','I have been a consuming a vegan diet for the past year. I made the decision for ethical reason due to my