d','','10-revision-v1','','','2016-10-12 15:03:26','2016-10-12 15:03:26','',10,'http://blog.calloftheforest.com/10-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(103,1,'2016-10-12 15:12:37','2016-10-12 15:12:37','<strong>I first heard about Mooji when I was in Rishikesh in Northern India earlier this year. Everyone I met was raving about his Satsangs, but unfortunately he left before I had a chance to hear him speak.</strong>\r\n\r\nWhen I returned to England I went to a gig in north London to see <a href=\"https://soundcloud.com/samgarrettmusic\">Sam Garrett</a> who turned out to be a Mooji devotee, his music is beautiful and he mentioned Mooji numerous times during the performance. So the seed had been sown¬†and I knew I needed to find out more about this <em>Mooji</em>. ¬†I discovered his Ashram was in Portugal and there was an upcoming 10 day silent retreat. The retreat was in such high demand that places were offered via lottery. ¬†I entered and to my surprise I got a place.\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-127\" src=\"http://blog.calloftheforest.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/montesahaja1-300x200.jpg\" sizes=\"85vw\" alt=\"montesahaja1\" />\r\n\r\nMoojis\' ashram is <a href=\"http://mooji.org/monte-sahaja/\">Monte Sahaja</a> in southern Portugal and every grain of sand is imbibed with love. He has created heaven on earth¬†where those inclined can spend time to discover their true nature. The format of the retreat is to attend 2 Satsangs a day, which last around 3 hours. ¬†It is ¬†during this Satsangs that¬†Mooji transmits to you the Truth. His style is wonderful, blending wisdom, humour and love and I found myself totally immersed. The rest of the day is spend in contemplation around the ashram.\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-106 size-medium\" src=\"http://blog.calloftheforest.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/shiva-300x200.jpg\" sizes=\"85vw\" alt=\"View from Shiva temple\" />\r\n\r\nHis teaching is simple and direct, simply that you are the Self and that you do not need any practices to achieve this, you need only recognise it. This appears too simple initially, but he guides you through the reactions of your mind to this Truth and as you sit in this space you begin to realise that this space is who you are, who you have always been and who you will always be, the timeless witness to the events which occur within your life and beyond.\r\n<blockquote>That which says:\r\n\r\nMy mind is too strong,\r\n\r\nis the mind itself.\r\n\r\nAn illusion strengthened by belief.</blockquote>\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-107\" src=\"http://blog.calloftheforest.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/lotusgarden2-300x300.jpg\" sizes=\"85vw\" alt=\"lotusgarden2\" />\r\n\r\nHere is a <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=8ui3vIvymDE\">recording</a> from one of his Satsangs','When I met Mooji ..','','publish','open','open','','when-i-met-mooji','','','2017-05-10 15:03:55','2017-05-10 15:03:55','',0,'http://blog.calloftheforest.com/?p=103',0,'post','',0),(104,1,'2016-10-12 15:09:42','2016-10-12 15:09:42','<p>Published in Barefoot Vegan magazine October 2016 edition.  <a href=\"http://www.barefootvegan.com/magazine.html\">Subscribe to Barefoot Vegan magazine</a></p>\r\n\r\n<img src=\"http://blog.calloftheforest.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/Barefoot-vegan-extract-212x300.jpg\" alt=\"Barefoot-vegan-extract\" class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-77\" sizes=\"(max-width: 212px) 85vw, 768px\" />','To Hell With Recycling I Want Reuse','','inherit','closed','closed','','10-revision-v1','','','2016-10-12 15:09:42','2016-10-12 15:09:42','',10,'http://blog.calloftheforest.com/10-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(105,1,'2016-10-12 15:12:37','2016-10-12 15:12:37','','When I met Mooji‚Ä¶.','','inherit','closed','closed','','103-revision-v1','','','2016-10-12 15:12:37','2016-10-12 15:12:37','',103,'http://blog.calloftheforest.com/103-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(106,1,'2016-10-12 15:21:25','2016-10-12 15:21:25','','Vie