204-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(232,1,'2017-02-14 15:06:09','2017-02-14 15:06:09','<dl>\r\n<dt>What is Butta?</dt>\r\n<dd><p>Butta is a plant based replacement for dairy butter; it looks and tastes just like traditional diary butter. It has a fat content of 75% and a melting point of 25¬∞C. Butta is made up of coconut oil (27%), Canola oil (26%) and Cocoa butter (21%).</p></dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<blockquote>Butta is a plant based replacement for dairy butter; it looks and tastes just like traditional diary butter</blockquote>\r\n\r\n<dt>Why Butta?</dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n<p>Switching to plant based is one of the <a href=\"http://www.spins.com/insights/trend-watch-2/plant-based-food/\" target=\"_blank\">fastest growing food trends</a>, Butta is an easy and convenient switch consumers can make to a plant based alternative.</p>\r\n<p class=\"image-wrapper\"><span class=\"fa-stack fa-lg\"><i class=\"fa fa-lightbulb-o fa-stack-2x\"></i></span>&nbsp;Did you know that in the UK veganism (a lifestyle that avoids using animals for human benefit) is the <a href=\"https://www.vegansociety.com/whats-new/news/find-out-how-many-vegans-are-great-britain\" target=\"_blank\">fastest growing lifestyle movement</a>?\r\n<img src=\"http://blog.calloftheforest.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/vegan.png\" alt=\"vegan\" width=\"111\" height=\"89\" class=\"wrapped-image\" />\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n</dd>\r\n\r\n<dd>\r\n<p class=\"image-wrapper\">\r\n<span class=\"fa-stack fa-lg\"><i class=\"fa fa-heart fa-stack-1x\"></i></span>&nbsp;Butta is a healthy option!<br />\r\n<em>Coconut oil</em> is good for cholesterol, its high Lauric acid content means that its energy is absorbed quickly giving a satisfying feeling of fullness. It also has antimicrobial properties which fight viruses and bacterial infections.\r\n<img src=\"http://blog.calloftheforest.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/cocoanut.png\" alt=\"cocoanut\" width=\"138\" height=\"89\" class=\"wrapped-image\"/>\r\n</p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p><em>Canola oil</em> has the 